          .key-benefits-text Make sure friends, family and customers can see your website. Hosting is what makes it possible for others to view your website over the Internet. Without it, youâ€™re the only one who will ever get a look. GoDaddy serves up:
            ul
              li One-click set-up
              li Unlimited storage and bandwidth
              li Scalability to fit your needs
              li 24/7 secure monitoring

